## ğŸµ OST & Sound Design

The soundtrack mixes **lo-fi jazz**, **ambient dread**, and **damaged audio filters** to simulate mental decay and emotional pressure. Sounds are intentionally limited â€” no music during key scenes. Silence becomes your enemy.

